These cookies are delicious! I made them both with and without the nuts... I liked them better without. I will definitely make them again next Christmas!

Rating: 4
Outstanding cookie, especially if you are a chocolate lover. I made a smaller cookie, about 2 tablespoons of dough instead of the 1/4 cup. The dough is quite sticky and very firm if refrigerated too long, as I did. I found it much easier to handle it by forming the dough into a log wrapped in aluminum foil. The dough is much easier to slice than to scoop out when thoroughly chilled.

